    "body": "Hi @prestonvanloon , we've been focusing on porting some other protocols due to the BLST gap but are back now. Is there a build flag to turn **off** the need for BLST? I understand it'll be slow, but I want to get a rough idea of order of magnitude perf degradation in the absence of optimized BLST. We'll be pursuing that path in parallel, but wanted to get a functional build working on the platform.",
